<p>&nbsp;</p> 
<h3 class="bonfire">Elden Ring Crimson Tears Notes &amp; Tips</h3> 
<ul> 
 <li>Whether your character is a mage or not, even at low Faith (such as 12 for <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Bestial Vitality" href="/Bestial+Vitality">Bestial Vitality</a>), Cerulean flasks are significantly more efficient at healing HP than Crimson are. However, Crimson flasks are much faster at healing. With this in mind, a Faith dip is worth considering for any build as a way to stretch flask usage.</li> 
 <li>Also known as Red Flask. Blue Flask is for FP.</li> 
</ul> 
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
